00:01:27.440 --> 00:01:32.160
your documents, your APIs, everything that you create and publish to Connect, all of

00:01:32.160 --> 00:01:36.559
those things are sandboxed apart from one another so that you can run those different

00:01:36.559 --> 00:01:40.080
versions of packages for all of your content.

00:01:40.080 --> 00:01:48.320
Fundamentally, though, if you're using Connect today, all of the content you publish there,

00:01:48.320 --> 00:01:55.120
